title: The Principal Upanishads Translated by Alan Jacobs 2012
description:
https://store.kobobooks.com/en-us/ebook/the-principal-upanishads-1?bookId=8c4eda1a-d7ec-4a8b-a466-ed05788c44e7

The Upanishads, the sacred writings of Hinduism, predate recorded history. Since they were revealed to the Rishis of the ancient Vedic civilization, many have come to regard them as the greatest of all books in the history of world religions - the kernel of the mystical and philosophical truths that are the basis of understanding religion today. Alan Jacobs accessible translation is presented in beautiful free verse.

ISBN:9781780284514
